        ],
        "from_reference": true,
        "call_context": "init"
      },
      {
        "signature": "void updateEgtmAtom3phInvDuty(float32 *requestDuty)",
        "behavior_description": "Immediate multi-channel duty update for the 3 complementary PWM phases. Copy the three percent values from requestDuty[0..2] into the module state dutyCycles[0..2] without scaling. Leave the trigger channel unchanged. Call the PWM driver’s immediate multi-channel duty update API with the dutyCycles array (percent) to apply new duties atomically at the next safe update point.",
