        "behavior_description": "Autonomous duty ramp for the 3 complementary phases: for each phase i in 0..2, add a fixed step (percent) to state.dutyCycles[i]. If a value exceeds 100.0, wrap it back to 0.0. After updating all three elements, pass the state.dutyCycles array directly (percent values) to the PWM driver’s immediate multi-channel duty update API to apply the change. Do not perform any STM-based timing here; periodic calling cadence is managed by the main loop.",
